headline: Factor4 and Oracle Micros Simphony Deliver Seamless Gift Card Integration to Elevate Customer Experience and Drive Revenue
summary: Factor4 is proud to announce the successful integration of its gift card platform with Oracle's industry-leading Micros Simphony point-of-sale (POS) system. This integration empowers restaurants, hotels, and retail operators to deliver a streamlined gift card experience directly within their existing POS environment—eliminating the need for third-party systems, external devices, or manual processes.
